---
description: Documentation standards
globs:
    - "*.md"
    - "docs/**/*.md"
    - "src/README.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

Keep docs accurate, concise, and command-copyable. Update README, environment,
testing, CI, security, and roadmap docs whenever behavior, architecture, tools,
security posture, or workflows change. Do not mark roadmap items complete
without objective evidence.
